At \ r VillaDawn.com, \ r we are firmly committed \ r to protecting your privacy.
We use the information we \ r collect about you only to complete a rental reservation or create listings for advertising \ r purposes.

Below you \ 'll find our privacy statement that \ r discloses our information gathering and dissemination \ r practices for this Web site, \ r VillaDawn.com. \ r \ r Your \ r Personal Information \ r We do not collect \ r personal information, such as e-mail address or telephone \ r number, from you on our site unless you inquire about \ r availability, make an online reservation or advertise \ r with VillaDawn.com, \ r we collect your personal information to answer your \ r inquiries and for billing purposes \ r only. \ r \ r Security \ r VillaDawn.com \ r has security measures in place to reasonably protect the \ r loss, misuse and alteration of the information under our \ r control. \ r Our online \ r reservation/payment form is secured by Geotrust. \ r \ r \ r \ r Children \ 's Guidelines \ r \ r We at \ r VillaDawn.com adhere \ r to the following concerning information provided by \ r children. \ r \ r 1.

NOT to intentionally collect online contact information \ r from children without prior parental consent or parental \ r notification, which will include an opportunity for the \ r parent to prevent use of the information and participation \ r in the activity.

Without prior parental consent online \ r information will only be used to respond directly to the \ r child \ 's request and will not be used for other purposes \ r without prior parental consent. \ r 2.
NOT to collect personally identifiable off-line contact \ r information without prior parental consent. \ r 3.
NOT to distribute to third parties any personally \ r identifiable information without prior parental consent. \ r 4.
NOT to give the ability to publicly post or otherwise \ r distribute personally identifiable contact information \ r without prior parental consent. \ r 5.

NOT to entice by the prospect of a special game, prize or \ r other activity, to divulge more information than is needed \ r to participate in the activity. \ r \ r Registration & Order Forms \ r When \ r you request availability and/or advertising information, we \ r collect your name, e-mail address and phone number.
This \ r allows us to respond to your request. \ r \ r
When \ r you submit advertising, we need to know your name, e-mail \ r address, mailing address, phone number, credit card number \ r and its expiration date.

This is all done on a secure \ r server or via the telephone. \ r When \ r you submit a review of a restaurant, we ask for your e-mail \ r address so we can contact you if we have questions about \ r your review.
If you are willing to be contacted via e-mail, \ r by other VillaDawn.com \ r users who may want to ask \ r more questions about the restaurant you reviewed, we will \ r include your e-mail address.
However, you can choose not to \ r have your e-mail address displayed with your review.
We also \ r ask for your name and phone number.

This is not published on \ r the Web site and is used only to verify the legitimacy of a \ r review. \ r We may also \ r use the information we collect to notify you occasionally \ r about new \ r VillaDawn.com \ r services, promotions and special offers we think you \ 'll find \ r valuable.

If you choose not to receive such notices, you can \ r send us an \ r \ r email \ r \ r and we will honor your request. \ r \ r Will \ r VillaDawn.com \ r disclose the information it \ r collects to outside parties? \ r VillaDawn.com \ r will not, under \ r any circumstances, disclose any information collected to any \ r outside parties. \ r \ r External Links \ r This site contains \ r links to other sites. \ r VillaDawn.com \ r is not responsible for the \ r privacy practices or the content of such Web sites. \ r \ r
In \ r Summary \ r VillaDawn.com \ r is committed to protecting your \ r privacy.

We use the information we collect on the site to \ r enhance your visit to our Web site and to occasionally send \ r you special offers and announcements. \ r Your \ r Consent \ r By using our Web \ r site, you permit \ r VillaDawn.com \ r to collect and use this \ r information as outlined above.
If we change our privacy \ r policy, we will post the changes on this page.

You will \ r always be aware of the information we collect, how we intend \ r to use it and under what circumstances we disclose it. \ r \ r \ r Contacting the Web Site \ r If you have any \ r questions about this privacy statement, the practices of \ r this site, or your dealings with this Web site, send us an \ r \ r email. \ r \ r

raw_html:
Privacy Policy

At 
VillaDawn.com,
we are firmly committed 
to protecting your privacy. We use the information we 
collect about you only to complete a rental reservation or create listings for advertising 
purposes. Below you'll find our privacy statement that 
discloses our information gathering and dissemination 
practices for this Web site,
VillaDawn.com.

Your 
Personal Information
We do not collect 
personal information, such as e-mail address or telephone 
number, from you on our site unless you inquire about 
availability, make an online reservation or advertise 
with VillaDawn.com, 
we collect your personal information to answer your 
inquiries and for billing purposes 
only. 

Security
VillaDawn.com 
has security measures in place to reasonably protect the 
loss, misuse and alteration of the information under our 
control.  
Our online 
reservation/payment form is secured by Geotrust. 

 

Children's Guidelines 

We at 
VillaDawn.com adhere 
to the following concerning information provided by 
children.

1. NOT to intentionally collect online contact information 
from children without prior parental consent or parental 
notification, which will include an opportunity for the 
parent to prevent use of the information and participation 
in the activity. Without prior parental consent online 
information will only be used to respond directly to the 
child's request and will not be used for other purposes 
without prior parental consent.
2. NOT to collect personally identifiable off-line contact 
information without prior parental consent.
3. NOT to distribute to third parties any personally 
identifiable information without prior parental consent.
4. NOT to give the ability to publicly post or otherwise 
distribute personally identifiable contact information 
without prior parental consent.
5. NOT to entice by the prospect of a special game, prize or 
other activity, to divulge more information than is needed 
to participate in the activity. 

Registration & Order Forms
When 
you request availability and/or advertising information, we 
collect your name, e-mail address and phone number. This 
allows us to respond to your request.

When 
you submit advertising, we need to know your name, e-mail 
address, mailing address, phone number, credit card number 
and its expiration date. This is all done on a secure 
server or via the telephone. 
When 
you submit a review of a restaurant, we ask for your e-mail 
address so we can contact you if we have questions about 
your review. If you are willing to be contacted via e-mail, 
by other VillaDawn.com
users who may want to ask 
more questions about the restaurant you reviewed, we will 
include your e-mail address. However, you can choose not to 
have your e-mail address displayed with your review. We also 
ask for your name and phone number. This is not published on 
the Web site and is used only to verify the legitimacy of a 
review. 
We may also 
use the information we collect to notify you occasionally 
about new 
VillaDawn.com 
services, promotions and special offers we think you'll find 
valuable. If you choose not to receive such notices, you can 
send us an 

email

and we will honor your request.

Will 
VillaDawn.com 
disclose the information it 
collects to outside parties?
VillaDawn.com
will not, under 
any circumstances, disclose any information collected to any 
outside parties. 

External Links
This site contains 
links to other sites. 
VillaDawn.com 
is not responsible for the 
privacy practices or the content of such Web sites.

In 
Summary
VillaDawn.com 
is committed to protecting your 
privacy. We use the information we collect on the site to 
enhance your visit to our Web site and to occasionally send 
you special offers and announcements. 
Your 
Consent
By using our Web 
site, you permit 
VillaDawn.com 
to collect and use this 
information as outlined above. If we change our privacy 
policy, we will post the changes on this page. You will 
always be aware of the information we collect, how we intend 
to use it and under what circumstances we disclose it.


Contacting the Web Site
If you have any 
questions about this privacy statement, the practices of 
this site, or your dealings with this Web site, send us an

email.
